CHOLERA - GUATEMALA
*******************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.healthnet.org/programs/promed.html>
See Also
Cholera - Belize (02) 980614093222
Cholera - Honduras (02) 980314214232
Date: Sun, 08 Nov 1998 21:28:00 -0600
From: "Jack E. Turner" <jeturner@idworld.net>
Source: news media Sun 8 Nov 1998

25 cases of cholera have been reported in Guatemala, the Public Health
Ministry there reported Friday. The Guatemalan government has increased
water-treatment efforts to prevent the disease from spreading.
(Reporter, James Anderson)
[Guatemala suffered severe damage to its health infastructure from Hurricane
Mitch. The outlook for cholera there is not good - Mod.JW
................................jw
